  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p><p>· Career development opportunities</p><p>· Remuneration package for right candidate</p><p>· Positive working environment</p><p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>The Account Executive will be responsible for :</p><p>Implementing and achieving the client’s fast paced tactical marketing plan.</p><p>Working closely with internal team members and clients</p><p>Devise campaign plans and tactics, brimming with ideas to inspire clients</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>Be the solid point of contact between client and agency</p><p>Campaign Management (Social, Digital, Content and beyond)</p><p>Execution and deliverables including reports, media and performance,  insights and learning</p><p>Ensure deadlines are met</p><p>We are a vibrant born in Singapore Creative Digital Agency, expanding our servicing team.</p><p><strong>Interested? Please write in with your resume.</strong></p><p><strong>Fresh graduates with a strong interest in marketing are welcome!</strong></p><p><strong>Preference will be given to those with 2 years of experience.</strong></p><p><strong>Only short-listed candidates will be notified for interviews</strong></p>",
